|俾斯麥級 || {{convert|251|m|ft|sp=us}} || {{convert|36|m|ft|sp=us}}{{sfn|Lenton|1966|p=47}} || 6.9比1 || {{convert|41,000|t|LT}} ||{{convert|138,000|shp|kW|lk=in|}}  ||{{convert|29|kn|km/h mph}} 
